---
import UntranslatedLayout from '~/layouts/UntranslatedLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '~/site.config';
---

<UntranslatedLayout title="Privacy Policy - Loreweaver" description="How Loreweaver handles your data.">
    <div class="pt-32 pb-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
            <div class="prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none text-foreground/80">
                <p class="text-lg mb-6">Last updated: February 22, 2026</p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-foreground">1. Introduction</h2>
                <p>
                    Loreweaver is operated by {siteConfig.legal?.entityName} (Org. nr. {siteConfig.legal?.orgNumber}).
                    This policy explains what data we collect and how we use it. The short version: your data is yours,
                    and we only use it to run the service you pay for.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-foreground">2. Data We Collect</h2>
                <p>
                    We collect only what you give us:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
                    <li><strong>Account information</strong> — your email address and display name when you sign up.</li>
                    <li><strong>Campaign content</strong> — the notes, characters, locations, items, and other material you create in Loreweaver.</li>
                    <li><strong>Session recordings</strong> — audio you upload for transcription.</li>
                    <li><strong>Usage data</strong> — basic server logs and product analytics needed to keep the service running and improve it (see Cookies & Analytics below).</li>
                </ul>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-foreground">3. How We Use Your Data</h2>
                <p>
                    Your data is used for one purpose: delivering the service you pay for. That means storing your campaigns,
                    processing your session audio, and running AI features against your content.
                </p>
                <p>
                    Loreweaver is a paid service. You are the customer, not the product. We do not sell your data,
                    serve ads, build advertising profiles, or share your information with third parties for marketing purposes.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-foreground">4. Data Residency</h2>
                <p>
                    All data is processed and stored on cloud infrastructure hosted exclusively within the EU/EEA.
                    Your data never leaves the EU/EEA.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-foreground">5. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
                <p>
                    We use cookies and lightweight product analytics exclusively to improve Loreweaver for paying customers.
                    For example: if an action you perform fails, we use that information to find and fix the problem.
                    If we notice that reaching a common feature takes three clicks, we use that to simplify the navigation.
                </p>
                <p>
                    This data is never used for advertising, profiling, or sold to third parties.
                    It exists for one reason: to make the product you pay for work better.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-foreground">6. Your Rights</h2>
                <p>
                    Under the GDPR, you have the right to:
                </p>
                <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2 mt-4">
                    <li><strong>Access</strong> your personal data and receive a copy of it.</li>
                    <li><strong>Correct</strong> inaccurate or incomplete data.</li>
                    <li><strong>Delete</strong> your data and account.</li>
                    <li><strong>Export</strong> your data in a portable format.</li>
                    <li><strong>Object</strong> to processing of your data.</li>
                </ul>
                <p class="mt-4">
                    To exercise any of these rights, contact us at the address below.
                </p>

                <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-12 mb-4 text-foreground">7. Contact</h2>
                <p>
                    Questions about this policy or your data? Reach us at
                    <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.contact?.email?.support}`} class="text-primary hover:underline">{siteConfig.contact?.email?.support}</a>.
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</UntranslatedLayout>
